<title>UK: Courtaulds Textiles H1 loss 8.5 mln stg.</title>
<headline>Courtaulds Textiles H1 loss 8.5 mln stg.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-09-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Second half to June 30</p>
<p>			   (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		8.4 loss	     vs 4.3 profit</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 5.2		    vs 5.2</p>
<p> Pretax		     8.5 loss	     vs 6.4 profit</p>
<p> Turnover		   481.0		  vs 515.3</p>
<p>NOTE - Analysts' forecasts were for the company to break even or make a small loss after exceptional charges. The textiles group said clothing order books indicate a better second half year-on-year and stretch fabrics are performing &quot;more strongly.&quot; But it said problems in lace would continue.</p>
